combtxt:ON 5/13/13 AT 8:25PM NIGHT-SHIFT OUT YARD RAIL CREW SECURED LOCOMOTIVE 424 AND RPRC CABOOSE #1 ON TR ACK 101 WRIGHT AVE STREET RUNNING JUST BEFORE DOT CROSSING 931747X AND WENT ON MEAL BREAK. AT 8:40 A  1997 DODGE RAM DRIVING WEST BOUND ON WRIGHT AVE WHICH PARALLELS STREET RUNNING TRACK 101 TOWARD DOT  CROSSING 931747X AT AN ESTIMATED SPEED OF 35 MPH. THE DRIVER DROVE HIS VEHICLE INTO THE B-END LEFT SIDE STEPS OF RPRC CABOOSE #1. THE B-END STEPS WERE PUSHED UNDER THE CABOOSE AND CRUMPLED THE FRONT:inci
